Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?[mms]=20SECURITY:=20Fix=20XSS=20in=20displaying?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20user-defined=20flags=20in=20dynamic=20mailbox=20view=20(Jo?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=C3=A3o=20Machado=20<geral@jpaulo.eu>).?=
